values.name: fromDict
values.comment:
Create a fast parser for a dictionary.

The parser succeeds with the longest matching key

    type Animal
        = Dog
        | Cat
        | Horse

    animal : Parser Animal
    animal =
        [ ( "doggo", Dog )
        , ( "kitty", Cat )
        , ( "horsey", Horse )
        ]
            |> Dict.fromList
            |> fromDict
